ure of the payments it is alleged that this conduct violated the foreign corrupt practices act and the antifraud issuer reporting books and records and internal controls provisions of the federal securities laws the complaint also alleges that faggioli and huff in their capacities as control persons violated the books and records and internal controls provisions of the securities laws in connection with the brazilian cash payments it is also alleged that nsp failed to disclose the payments to brazilian customs agents in its filings with the commission the civil injunctive action which was filed in the united states district court for the district of utah alleges that nsp violated sections b a ba bb and a of the exchange act and rules b b a and a thereunder and that faggioli and huff violated sections ba and bb as control persons pursuant to section a of the exchange act nsp faggioli and huff without admitting or denying the allegations of the complaint have consented to the entry of final judgments that would enjoin each of the defendants from future violations of the abovestated provisions and would order nsp to pay a civil penalty of  and faggioli and huff to each pay a civil penalty of  sec complaint   httpwwwsecgovlitigationlitreleaseslrhtm home  previous page modified 7   section  huff nicholas and huff craig hardcover 7 powells books cart    my account    wish list    help     77 hello  login all books new used advanced menu browse new arrivals bestsellers award winners signed preorders signed editions digital audio books daily dose newsletters see all subjects used staff picks staff picks best books of 7 so far staff top fives  picks of the month boox indiespensable  global books to read before you die  women to read before you die  books to read before you die gifts  gift cards gift cards  egift cards powells souvenirs journals  notebooks games socks sell books sell books online sell books in our stores blog events find a store dont miss vacation education s